==工業上的手性助劑==
手性助劑通常是可靠且多功能的，使得大量的單一鏡像異構物可在省時的方式下合成。因此，手性助劑經常會在藥物開發的初期階段被使用。<ref name="Glorius review" />

===Tipranavir===
HIV蛋白酶抑制劑{{link-en|Tipranavir|Tipranavir}}，被銷售用於愛滋病的治療。Tipranavir在藥物化學用途中的第一鏡像選擇性，包括有機酮試劑的共軛加成手性[[麥可加成反應|麥可受體]]。<ref>{{cite journal | author = Turner, S. T. et al. | title = Tipranavir (PNU-140690): A Potent, Orally Bioavailable Nonpeptidic HIV Protease Inhibitor of the 5,6-Dihydro-4-hydroxy-2-pyrone Sulfonamide Class | year = 1998 | journal = [[J._Med._Chem.|J. Med. Chem.]] | volume = 41 | pages = 3467–3476 | doi = 10.1021/jm9802158}}</ref>Michael受體中的噁唑烷酮控制著此兩立體中心中其中一個的立體性。最後，商業用途的Tipranavir不具有手性助劑，而是由[[不對稱氫化|不對稱氫化]]反應產生立體結構中心。<ref>{{cite book |last=Caron |first=Stéphane |editor-first=Stéphane |editor-last=Caron |title=Practical Synthetic Organic Chemistry |url=https://archive.org/details/practicalsynthet00caro |publisher=John Wiley & Sons, Inc. |year=2011 |pages=[https://archive.org/details/practicalsynthet00caro/page/n669 666]–670 |chapter=Chapter 15: Synthetic Route Development of Selected Contemporary Pharmaceutical Drugs |isbn=978-0-470-03733-1}}</ref>

[[Image:Tipranavir_routes.png|center]]<br />
{{center| Tipranavir形成關鍵立體中心的合成策略。}}

===Atorvastatin===
[[阿托伐他汀|阿托伐他汀]]的鈣鹽在市場上的銷售名為立普妥（Lipitor）是一種降低血中膽固醇的藥物。Atorvastatin在藥物化學用途中的第一鏡像選擇性依賴著非鏡像選擇性的醇醛縮合反應，而反應中使用手性酯來建立醇的兩個立體中心的其中一個。<ref>{{cite journal | author = Roth, B. D. ''et al.' '| title = Inhibitors of Cholesterol Biosynthesis.  3. Tetrahydro-4-hydroxy-6-[2-(  lH-pyrrol-l-yl)ethyl]-2H-pyran-2-one  Inhibitors of HMG-CoA Reductase.  2.  Effects of Introducing Substituents at Positions Three and Four of the Pyrrole Nucleus  | year = 1991 | journal = [[J._Med._Chem.|J. Med. Chem.]] | volume = 34 | pages = 357–366 | doi = 10.1021/jm00105a056}}</ref>Atorvastatin在商業用途上因容易獲得的[[異抗壞血酸|異抗壞血酸]]而被發揚光大。<ref>{{cite book |authors = Jie Jack Li, Douglas S. Johnson, Drago R. Sliskovic, Bruce D. Roth |title=Contemporary Drug Synthesis |url = https://archive.org/details/contemporarydrug00liji |publisher=John Wiley & Sons, Inc. |year=2004 |pages=[https://archive.org/details/contemporarydrug00liji/page/n126 113]–125 |chapter=Chapter 9. Atorvastatin Calcium (Lipitor) |isbn=0-471-21480-9}}</ref>

